94ccdba9-f486-42db-8f63-8ef20634364e.title: Note
94ccdba9-f486-42db-8f63-8ef20634364e.text:
interactions with the doors with the X on them,
the big house with stairs.

cb438f27-7fe4-428e-9230-40e2f6859e61.text:
The door won't open.
You notice a black cross on the door.

6534e6b7-dbbf-478e-bfe5-4bd5d3059d55.title: Mourner
6534e6b7-dbbf-478e-bfe5-4bd5d3059d55.text:
I'd stand away from there. That black cross means that
house has been touched by the plague.

options.text: But I think a kidnap victim is in here.
I fear not a mere plague.

9c3086c8-450e-4037-a1a2-ee86ab0c843f.title: <player>
9c3086c8-450e-4037-a1a2-ee86ab0c843f.text: I fear not a mere plague.

9ccd8f50-f588-4c8d-952b-69ce7d54eaf8.title: Mourner
9ccd8f50-f588-4c8d-952b-69ce7d54eaf8.text:
That's irrelevant. You don't have clearance to go in
there.

dffc668f-1de1-4912-a514-478c19bfbee2.title: Mourner
dffc668f-1de1-4912-a514-478c19bfbee2.text:
Well you'd need to apply to the head mourner, or I
suppose Bravek the city warder.

b2a86dcb-594b-4302-a0de-2e62daabdb26.title: Mourner
b2a86dcb-594b-4302-a0de-2e62daabdb26.text: I wouldn't get your hopes up though.

16a4a2f5-499a-40ba-9ef8-d5f264be13ac.title: <player>
16a4a2f5-499a-40ba-9ef8-d5f264be13ac.text: But I think a kidnap victim is in here.

1b62a4d4-99d0-482a-92bf-c3ef10c68f8d.title: Mourner
1b62a4d4-99d0-482a-92bf-c3ef10c68f8d.text:
Sounds unlikely, even kidnappers wouldn't go in there. 
Even if someone is in there, they're probably dead by
now.

9df55f3d-3ee5-4ec0-be2c-7d2d8e14d514.title: Mourner
9df55f3d-3ee5-4ec0-be2c-7d2d8e14d514.text: You don't have clearance to go in there.

6116b33e-a834-4efa-a2a3-17567fd70963.text:
The door won't open.
You notice a black cross on the door.

5b0fe58a-3632-400f-891f-5273af3b3241.title: Mourner
5b0fe58a-3632-400f-891f-5273af3b3241.text:
I'd stand away from there. That black cross means that
house has been touched by the plague.

fc07ddd8-b833-40c6-8bff-8e11439fd15d.title: <player>
fc07ddd8-b833-40c6-8bff-8e11439fd15d.text: I have a warrant from Bravek to enter here.

bfb6c8c8-1f2c-4bbb-97b4-3df94629c14f.title: Mourner
bfb6c8c8-1f2c-4bbb-97b4-3df94629c14f.text:
I'd stand away from there. That black cross means that
house has been touched by the plague.

3b2e5b2b-24fc-431a-b11d-2d5277d62b8e.title: Mourner
3b2e5b2b-24fc-431a-b11d-2d5277d62b8e.text: This is highly irregular. Please wait...

838cc288-ef09-4f37-ada2-de48ae7ac6a5.text:
You wait until the mourner's back is turned and sneak into the
building.

680855cd-b1a8-4141-9e38-68e8c504fb1b.title: Note
680855cd-b1a8-4141-9e38-68e8c504fb1b.text:
Dialogue between Mourners
Mourner 1: Hey... I've got someone here with a warrant from Bravek, what should we do?
Mourner 2: Well you can't let them in...
